      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump, which is geometrically representative of the Class II CPB device under assessment. Reynolds number range and non-Newtonian blood rheology conditions match COU operating envelope. Minor geometric differences between generic pump and specific device addressed through sensitivity analysis showing < 8% variation in RH. Gradation 2 met for MRL 2."
    },
    {
