      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; commercial solver documentation sufficient.",
      "rationale": "At Model Risk Level 2, explicit numerical solver error quantification beyond code verification is not required. The commercial solver's iterative convergence is monitored via residual criteria (< 1e-5 for all equations) and mass balance (< 0.01%). These standard convergence checks satisfy the MRL 2 expectation without formal solver error budgeting."
    },
    {
