      "rationale": "Simulation setup reviewed by a second qualified CFD engineer independent of the primary analyst. Boundary conditions, turbulence model selection (SST k-omega), and hemolysis model implementation verified against published protocol. No discrepancies identified. Formal use-error quantification not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
