      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; model form selection justified by literature precedent.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model with power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger correlation) selected based on published consensus for blood pump CFD at MRL 2. Literature survey confirms this model form is widely used for centrifugal pump hemolysis prediction. Formal model form error quantification deferred per MRL 2 scoping."
    },
